  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Text message reminders will improve adherence to lab tests in adolescent liver transplant
      recipients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Adolescent patients who received a liver transplant will be recruited to participate in
      receiving text message reminders for lab tests. They will be send de-identified messages
      according to their required lab schedule. The investigators will monitor their adherence to
      lab tests as well as medication and clinic visits. They will also have a questionnaire about
      their medical regimen before and at the end of the study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
